io.spine.tools.protoc

Class Method

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.spine.value.ValueHolder<java.lang.String>
      • io.spine.value.StringTypeValue
        • io.spine.tools.protoc.Method
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    @Immutable
public class Method
extends io.spine.value.StringTypeValue
    A generated Java method source code.

    SPI users are responsible for checking that the content of the method is properly formatted and contains all the required modifiers, comments, and Javadoc.

    The actual compilation of the generated method is performed as a part of the compilation of other Protobuf-generated sources.
